      "description": "Available for the discerning driver is this E46 M3, featuring the legendary S54 3.2L inline-six power plant with individual throttle bodies and high-pressure double VANOS. This chassis remains rigid, having undergone essential rear subframe reinforcement to mitigate common fatigue points. Power is delivered through a crisp 6-speed Getrag manual transmission to a limited-slip differential, ensuring optimal torque distribution. The suspension geometry is dialed in with upgraded bushings and dampers, providing telepathic feedback through the hydraulic steering rack. Recent preventative maintenance includes rod bearing replacement and a valve adjustment, ensuring the high-revving valvetrain operates within factory tolerances. A mechanically sound example ready for spirited apex-hunting.",
